An '''Authority Cash Voucher''' was a debt-receipt used in the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] in the years directly preceding the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The amount due to a being was magnetically entered into a plastic [[Datacard/Legends|datacard]] that was used in lieu of currency within the CSA. Authority Cash Vouchers were obtainable at [[Authority Currency Exchange]]s.

{{Tech-stub}}

